title: THE RED TEN 003 (2013) (ComixTribe) (Digital) (Darkness-Empire)
description:
The Red Ten #3

And then there were eight... Fear mounts after a second shocking death suggests that THE ALLIANCE are not alone on the island. Was this the Oxymoron's brilliant plan all along... or is something even more sinister afoot? Another hero falls, and more shocking revelations in this pivotal third issue.

Published by ComixTribe
Written by Tyler James
Pencils: Cesar Feliciano
Inks: Vic Moya
Colored by: Gus Ucha
Edited by: Steve Colle, Steve Forbes 

Genres: Action/Adventure, Superhero

34 Pages
Digital Release Date: 06/26/2013
Age Rating: 15+ Only
